title: NFL ATL: Week 5 recap

description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus  and Chris Wesseling recap all of the Week 5 action. Don’t miss the analysis and key takeaways from each game. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.
